{"name":"ノクティス・ルシス・チェラム","nameCn":"诺克提斯·路西斯·凯拉姆","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/db/6d/20227_crt_RZR9z.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>诺克提斯·路西斯·凯拉姆</li><li><span>别名: </span>Noctis Lucis Caelum</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>诺克特(ノクト)</li><li><span>性别: </span>男</li><li><span>生日: </span>8月30日</li><li><span>身高: </span>176cm</li><li><span>年龄: </span>20岁</li><li><span>喜欢的事情: </span>钓鱼、刷新游戏的最高记录</li>","detail":"本作主角，昵称诺克特（Noct ノクト）。以水晶守护路西斯王国，王国的下一任国王。个性冷静，因感情的变化，眼睛和头发的颜色也有所改变（瞳孔从蓝色变为红色）。根据水晶的力量操纵多种武器（在第2部预告片中使用了超过20把），但都以剑为主要武器。除了武器，也有一种是挥动手指间的光线来阻挡子弹的“盾”。诺克特可以依照武器所到之处瞬间移动到武器旁，所以是一种不限场地的战斗风格。在宣传短片中以一人力战众多持枪的士兵。名中的“Noctis”为拉丁文中之“夜”，“Lucis”为拉丁文之中的“光”，姓氏“Caelum”为“天空”，全名可能隐喻“夜空之光”。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/1928","name":"FINAL FANTASY XV","nameCn":"最终幻想15","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/5b/ce/1928_CCZFM.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"鈴木達央","castHref":"/person/5031","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/e3/27/5031_seiyu_anidb.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/176292","name":"BROTHERHOOD FINAL FANTASY XV","nameCn":"最终幻想15 兄弟情","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/0a/bf/176292_MzvsV.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"鈴木達央","castHref":"/person/5031","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/e3/27/5031_seiyu_anidb.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/216537","name":"DISSIDIA FINAL FANTASY NT","nameCn":"最终幻想 纷争NT","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/f6/c4/216537_Ai7KK.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/298123","name":"FINAL FANTASY XV -The Dawn Of The Future-","nameCn":"最终幻想15 未来黎明","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/93/d0/298123_7Rw3P.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/113037","name":"FINAL FANTASY Record Keeper","nameCn":"最终幻想 记录守护者","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/9a/48/113037_6Z1o1.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/176296","name":"KINGSGLAIVE FINAL FANTASY XV","nameCn":"最终幻想15 王者之剑","cover":"//lai